<div class="sourceCode" id="cb4"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb4-1"><a href="#cb4-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>session <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> shiny<span class="sc">::</span>MockShinySession<span class="sc">$</span><span class="fu">new</span>()</span>

<span id="cb4-5"><a href="#cb4-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>lang <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="st">&quot;fr&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb4-6"><a href="#cb4-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb4-7"><a href="#cb4-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># Generate all inputs as in the Shiny application</span></span>
<span id="cb4-8"><a href="#cb4-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>countries <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">c</span>(<span class="st">&quot;all&quot;</span>, datasets[[<span class="st">&quot;countries_mortalities_list&quot;</span>]])</span>
<span id="cb4-9"><a href="#cb4-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb4-10"><a href="#cb4-10" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>mortalities <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">data.frame</span>(</span>
<span id="cb4-11"><a href="#cb4-11" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>        <span class="co"># country = golem::get_golem_options(&#39;countries_mortalities_list&#39;),</span></span>
<span id="cb4-12"><a href="#cb4-12" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>        <span class="at">country =</span> datasets[[<span class="st">&quot;countries_mortalities_list&quot;</span>]],</span>
<span id="cb4-13"><a href="#cb4-13" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>        <span class="at">yearsimubegin =</span> <span class="fl">0.1</span>,</span>
<span id="cb4-14"><a href="#cb4-14" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>        <span class="at">yearsimuend =</span> <span class="fl">0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-15"><a href="#cb4-15" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>      )</span>
<span id="cb4-16"><a href="#cb4-16" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb4-17"><a href="#cb4-17" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>mortalities</span>

<span id="cb4-28"><a href="#cb4-28" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 10       Spain           0.1</span></span>

<span id="cb4-32"><a href="#cb4-32" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt;    yearsimuend</span></span>
<span id="cb4-33"><a href="#cb4-33" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 1          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-34"><a href="#cb4-34" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 2          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-35"><a href="#cb4-35" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 3          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-36"><a href="#cb4-36" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 4          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-37"><a href="#cb4-37" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 5          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-38"><a href="#cb4-38" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 6          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-39"><a href="#cb4-39" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 7          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-40"><a href="#cb4-40" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 8          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-41"><a href="#cb4-41" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 9          0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-42"><a href="#cb4-42" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 10         0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-43"><a href="#cb4-43" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 11         0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-44"><a href="#cb4-44" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 12         0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-45"><a href="#cb4-45" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co">#&gt; 13         0.5</span></span>
<span id="cb4-46"><a href="#cb4-46" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb4-47"><a href="#cb4-47" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># # build from sliders in interface </span></span>
<span id="cb4-48"><a href="#cb4-48" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># expand grid using full_join</span></span>
<span id="cb4-49"><a href="#cb4-49" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>anthropogenic_mortality <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">full_join</span>(data_hsi_nmax <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-50"><a href="#cb4-50" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="fu">distinct</span>(year) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-51"><a href="#cb4-51" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="fu">mutate</span>(<span class="at">by =</span> <span class="dv">1</span>),</span>
<span id="cb4-52"><a href="#cb4-52" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>          data_hsi_nmax <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-53"><a href="#cb4-53" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="fu">distinct</span>(country) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-54"><a href="#cb4-54" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="fu">mutate</span>(<span class="at">by =</span> <span class="dv">1</span>), <span class="at">by =</span> <span class="st">&quot;by&quot;</span>) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-55"><a href="#cb4-55" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">select</span>(<span class="sc">-</span>by) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-56"><a href="#cb4-56" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="fu">mutate</span>(<span class="at">h2 =</span> <span class="dv">0</span>) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-57"><a href="#cb4-57" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">collect</span>() <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-58"><a href="#cb4-58" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="co"># Join with table of mortalities</span></span>
<span id="cb4-59"><a href="#cb4-59" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">left_join</span>(mortalities, <span class="at">by =</span> <span class="st">&quot;country&quot;</span>) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-60"><a href="#cb4-60" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">mutate</span>(</span>
<span id="cb4-61"><a href="#cb4-61" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="at">h1 =</span> <span class="fu">case_when</span>(</span>
